These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: bluemaster, montecristo, oliveros, swisher
1. Cigar:montecristo is in an odd position##4
2. Cigar:swisher is between Cigar:bluemaster and Cigar:montecristo##2
3. Cigar:swisher is on the right of Cigar:bluemaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | swisher | montecristo | oliveros |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: chess, card-games, sudoku, rock-climbing
1. Hobby:chess is on the left of Hobby:rock-climbing##1
2. Hobby:card-games is in an odd position##4
3. Hobby:card-games is on the left or right of Hobby:chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | card-games | chess | rock-climbing | sudoku |

 #################################
 
