.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Flower: azalea, dahlia, rose, tulip
1. Flower:dahlia == Flower:dahlia##1
2. Flower:tulip is on the left or right of Flower:rose##3
3. Flower:rose is on the far left or far right##3
4. Flower:azalea is in an even position##4
5. Flower:tulip is on the left of Flower:dahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Flower   | rose | tulip | dahlia | azalea |

